{"tid":824188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊後花園遭蹂躪","createTime":"2018-09-17T03:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T05:41:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f355b3c148260fa05a76769e9364085f39bb54","tid":824188,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180917/large/a1404a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180917%2Flarge%2Fa1404a.gif&h=8a80209c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯家驊個後花園俾山竹吹到斷樹（箭嘴示）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n山竹來襲下，唔少人屋企都滲水漏水，冇爆玻璃已經好好，行會成員兼民主思路召集人湯家驊（Ronny）位於大埔嘅大宅都遭殃，偌大嘅花園有一半樹冧咗，佢就喺facebook開post貼圖話好彩，「尚算幸運，只是超過花園一半樹幹斷落、屋內不時停電&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n鄰居斷樹「吹過嚟要我執埋」<br />\n<br />\n相片可見本來設計典雅嘅花園畀山竹吹一吹，凌亂不堪，八方問過Ronny，佢話屋企位處山谷，以往打風都冇咁應，所以連米字形膠紙都冇貼，誰不知今次山竹好鬼勁，所以花園嚴重受襲，雖然啲樹唔係Ronny自家種，但都對咗幾十年㗎，自然都有感情㗎，禍不單行嘅係連隔籬屋啲樹都斷咗，「吹埋過嚟，要我幫佢執埋」，唔好彩嘅係佢份家居保唔包花園位置，所以要自己掏錢維修，「希望唔會使太多（錢）啦」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180917/20501229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F20501229&d=Sha41oWSewozM7Uf%2BQdNNWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=d8a7b6ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F20501229&h=62f6ed23\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180917/20501229</a>"},{"pid":"e1a70bcac1b4e4de7cdb8996669906e4e2f703ed","tid":824188,"uid":33668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"奶共人事住得真係好"},{"pid":"6dfa663095ecf9a85378418964e1169fee0659f3","tid":824188,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"可以去雪廠街d酒店暫住"},{"pid":"898c1e5cb40d83609465d16d921ce0c5991bc549","tid":824188,"uid":33668,"